data.description: This great 3/2 low maintenance brick ranch style home is ready for you to call it “home sweet home.” This inviting home features a popular open floor plan. Fresh paint throughout and recently renewed kitchen countertops. The hand scraped hardwood floors are beautiful and definitely a plus to any home. The spacious den or bonus room is perfect for entertaining guest and for family gatherings. New insulated windows have been recently installed as well per seller. In addition to this spacious home there is a 900 square ft approximately detached 2/1 apartment. This would be perfect for an in-law suite or for extra income. There are two storage sheds on the property and the spacious back yard is fenced in and perfect for pets and children to run and play safely. Please do not delay and make your appointment to see this home today!    Upscale security system to remain with the home. This is a great neighborhood with the best neighbors who look out for each other per seller.
